sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant CHAT as Chat Backend
  participant TAPI as Tool API/Registry
  participant TRUN as Tool Runner
  participant MCP as MCP API/Client

  U->>CHAT: Prompt requiring tool action
  CHAT->>TAPI: Resolve available tool
  TAPI-->>CHAT: Allowed tool set (owner/admin constrained)
  CHAT->>TRUN: Execute tool call
  opt MCP-backed tool
    TRUN->>MCP: Discover/connect tool server
    MCP-->>TRUN: Tool capability + auth context
  end
  TRUN-->>CHAT: Tool output
  CHAT-->>U: Final response

  Note over TRUN,MCP: Needs Verification: deny behavior and credential failure semantics
